In order to build and run this project you need to install OpenCV from here:
http://sourceforge.net/projects/opencvlibrary/files/opencv-win/2.2/

download the following file:
OpenCV-2.2.0-win32-vs2010.exe

Make sure you select OpenCV binaries to be added to the path during install.

The project assumes your OpenCV install will be in c:\OpenCV2.2
